Hardcore / Punk / Emo / Screamo

Some of their members also played in City of Caterpillar, who played a kind of an unorthodox gloomy screamo, and Mannequin, a grunge-influence punk rock band.

After the demise of both pg.99 & City of Caterpillar in 2003, Malady was formed featuring members of both bands. Several members of pg.99 currently play in thebands Haram and Pygmy Lush.
